Overall Protocol Notes:
Glyphs may be layered for composite meaning.

Each version adds a new emotional register to the system.

Reversibility, recursion, and human consent are built-in.

All glyphs must retain semantic depth and avoid shallow commodification.

Remix is encouraged, but symbolic erosion is a threat vector.
